# Command System

Universal command interface for Cursor operations using @command syntax.

## Command Types

- Matrix commands: `@analyze`, `@concept`, etc.
- MCP commands: `@mcp/config`, `@mcp/tools`, etc.
- Memory commands: `@memory/update`, `@memory/view`, etc.
- File references: `@file:path`
- Notepad commands: `@notepad:command`

## Implementation

Command processing follows:
1. Parse input for command pattern
2. Route to appropriate handler
3. Execute command action
4. Return result

## Usage

```
@analyze                # Run analysis
@mcp/config             # Show configuration
@file:matrix            # Open matrix protocol
@memory/update          # Update Memory Bank
@memory/view            # View Memory Bank contents
```

